						               													<description>Smoke &amp;amp; Mirrors (SnM) Expansion reminds us that Aristeia! is pure spectacle, a Show for Maya where everything is crafted and treated for the audience&amp;rsquo;s consumption.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A Father-Inquisitor set to burn heretics, an Eastern Warlock that tortures his enemies with their worst nightmares, a bloodthirsty half-breed Wulver and a smoke throwing robot. Fantastic Characters that will rise the audience levels.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Murtair, Close combat fighter that can use Damage he&amp;rsquo;s suffered to his own benefit. Offensive profile, given that his Defense is low, and he has no easy way to Disengage (his bloodthirstiness keeps him from leaving the combat).&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Kozmo, Support-scorer that protects her team by blocking Line of Sight with her Smoke. Even though she has a very good Defense, she is not a tank.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Padre Inquisidor Mendoza, The Automatic Skill Sanatur a Deo, couple with his Damage capabilities, turn him into an off-tank. If the rival Team has no appropriate counter, he can also work as a tank, because is hard to send him to the Infirmary.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;T&amp;aacute;ow&amp;ugrave;, Control Support, very aggressive that works mainly with the enemy&amp;rsquo;s card pool. In addition to that, he is always threating to impose the Immobilized State very easily.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A new type of token that affects the Hexadome Spaces is added:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Smoke. Smoke affects Space visibility, blocking Line of Sight without hindering movement.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A new State is added:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Burning. While the blue side of a burning token is up, the player rolls an Orange Dice. For every success, The Character receives a 1 Damage, while for each Special the Character receives a new Burning token.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Smoke and Mirrors is not a full game. Need a copy of Aristeia! to play.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
